They said, “What are you?”

35:11.038 --> 35:14.108
And he said, “I am a Christian,” though
he had murdered.

35:14.108 --> 35:17.869
Then they gave him the Bible, “All right,
put your hand on the Bible and say you are

35:17.869 --> 35:21.388
a Christian.”

