36:57.479 --> 37:02.628
do like this; don’t do like that.”  But
despite that I have seen, I’m surprised

37:02.628 --> 37:07.829
that Hindus are very meek people because the
responsibility is left to themselves, not

37:07.829 --> 37:13.138
on an organization.   If you have murdered
